Package com.intellij.debugger.ui.tree

Interface NodeDescriptorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeDescriptorFactoryImpl, NodeManagerImpl

    public interface NodeDescriptorFactory
    creates descriptors if descriptor was already created in current context (that is location in debugee code) returns that descriptor else creates new descriptor and restores it's representation properties from history
